The paper focuses on the optimization of deep learning models, which is a core topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper specifically mentions image classification tasks, which suggests that it may also fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the generalization of optimization strategies, which is a topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of stochastic optimization methods may also place the paper in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the automation of benchmarking, which could be relevant to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
